name: TrialDirector Object Load List
summary: Learn about .OLL files and view a list of programs that open them.

windows.name: Open over 400 file formats with File Viewer Plus.Free Download

content: NOTE: The OLL file contains nine fields, which include Record Type, Document ID, Item ID, Page Number, Description, Volume Label, Path, Filename, and Special Field.

description: Load file used by TrialDirector, a program used to create, organize, and present trial information; contains ASCII text used to establish relationship for multi-page TrialDirector documents and determine which tab is associated with each item.
